3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as the paper introduces context awareness to augment local feature descriptors. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possibility as the paper deals with image representation and matching. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possibility as the paper deals with geometric matching applications.
